                <pl:parameter name="message" value="-&#10;--&gt; Completed retrieve DeRegistration Case Events for RTL&#10;--&gt;SEQUENCE -  Extract DeRegistration Case Events Sequence&#10;--&gt;VIEW -  Extract Extract DeRegistration Case Events  View&#10;--&gt;CIRCUIT - ccbc_rtl_file_first_day&#10;----------------------------------------------------------------------------------"/>
